phrases: What is with those clothes, anyway?
Is she some pop star from the'70s?
Unlike you, Kumin's a pure, straightforward person untainted by this day and age!
Big words for a grade schooler.
You sort of look like a grade schooler.
The bursts of sunlight and gamma rays are threatening me with death!
Her eighth-grader syndrome is more like second-grader syndrome now.
Did you say something, Fake Summer?!
I did not say a word!
It sure sounded like you lumped me together with that crew-cut kid!
Who are you calling crew-cut kid?!
The grade schoolers have two options: silence or death!
Come with Rikka on our summer vacation.
Told you she is like a grade schooler.
Watch the trees in the distance!
At times like this I must summon the wisdom of the Mabinogion
to purge myself of this malady!
Nibutani, there is a restroom that way.
I think a guy going there with a girl would raise a few eyebrows.
I would sooner face death than accept help from a fake!
We do not have long to go.
Aided by my enemy in my greatest moment of distress.
It is obvious as hell where you are looking.
Are not you going to react in some way?!
Or have you got motion sickness too?
Then why are you so quiet?
The world is spinning like a carousel of death!
I told you to shut up!
Why do I have to take care of her?
You make a good class rep.
You are good at taking care of others.
Does not mean I like it!
This is all'cos you had to barf all over us!
By the way, is she all right?
Want to come along to hang out?
Maybe there is something here for her.
You know, the usual kind of thing!
Maybe her sweetheart from junior high went to a different high school,
but they waited for each other in a kind of long-distance relationship...
In other words, a battlefield of love?
Battlefield of Love is a powerful barrier spell...
It is such a big house!
Thank you for coming all this way.
Takanashi always does so much for us,
and now you have even invited us into your home.
I am still worried that we are imposing on you.
So, Rikka's still pretending to be a pirate?
The things kids do these days.
I hoped she would have grown up a little...
let us give them the Dark Brown Liquid!
Please accept this small token of our appreciation.
Ah, please, do not worry about it.
You do not have much stuff here.
I am engaged in communications with the other side of the Ethereal Horizon.
I attempted to move it to my current base,
but the Priestess denied me permission.
Let me say it in your language.
I sense an unusual aura around here.
This is not a real base of mine either.
I used it only because of the Overseers.
A lone house where nothing ever happens.
However, there is a barrier here that negates the existence of the Ethereal Horizon.
Mental assaults and pressure were extensive.
That is why I ran away.
I do not really get it, but does that mean something happened?
To break down this barrier, I needed...
the power of the Wicked Eye.
I will leave your luggage here.
Also, your friends are going to the beach.
Please do not make them worry.
That is quite the bikini, Forest Summer!
This was the only one I had, so I thought I would give it a try...
There is a monstrous kraken in this sea!
We should test the power of our marine magical gear by bringing its death upon it!
With that equipment, you get a 3.88 movement speed multiplier until you reach the water.
You have not talked much, ha
Why are you listening to her?!
Hey, why are you following me around?
What is this supposed to mean?
I could not care less about its name.
It is time we traveled to the Ethereal Horizon's cluster point.
This camouflage is necessary to escape the Priestess's watchful eyes.
So it comes down to this?
My whole body aches like death!
That sacred light got the better of me!
That is because you went running around all day
without even putting any sunscreen on.
But at least my Black Seal is now complete!
They said we should eat this together.
It was exactly three years ago.
Rikka was so little, Dad did not want to tell her.
So for her, he passed away suddenly and without warning.
It is probably because of that that she still does not even try to accept his death.
She stubbornly refuses to come here.
She left us with Dad's family.
so he could not accept Rikka no matter what.
I had to leave because of my work as well,
so for the past two years, nothing's changed.
I must find the Ethereal Horizon.
To overcome this barrier, I needed
the power of the Wicked Eye.
It is what I do for a living, after all.
Now that you mention it, Takanashi's boxed lunches always look delicious!
They have been the talk of our class!
You work in such a great restaurant!
How could it be any worse?!
I should have expected this from the Priestess even my Master fears!
Her powers of commandment are amazing!
That reminds me, where is Rikka?
I will go take a look for her.
The Wicked Eye is the strongest.
It seems you have suffered the Priestess's mental assaults.
So that is what you feared?
I am still the former Dark Flame Master, you know.
I thought you wanted to look for the Ethereal Horizon.
Mom and Tooka and Granny and Grandpa all...
That is why I am here.
Too I mean the Priestess must be on high alert.
It will not be easy to escape.
When do you want to go?
Once you make it to the tree, go around the right so that it conceals you.
I do not even have shoes, you know.
I did not expect you would help her.
Let us go to where I hid the Rad Zwei, Hell Brown!
You just had to, did not you?
The Dark Flame Master's the greatest!
The Dark Flame Master's the greatest!
I told you not to call me that.
But the Wicked Eye is even greater.
Rikka and Togashi did not come back in the end.
The things people do for love.
I would say it is just a matter of time.
But I saw him that night.
I could see Dad beyond the horizon.
That is why I am sure he is still here.
He is watching over this place, and me as well, from the other side of the horizon.
I could not agree with that, but neither could I deny it.
My base, where Dad and I and everyone else were all together.
